This is a mirror of http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=3692

quickhl.vim support highlight for

* multiple keywords manually specified via command or keymap.
  also provide operator for highlight.
* `tag` in ctags generated file(defult, underlined)
* automatically higlight word under cursor(=`<cword>`).

quickhl.vim not provide any keymap by default(its my preference)
See help.

### Github
https://github.com/t9md/vim-quickhl

